  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Accounts Assistant (AP & Costing)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Salary: Up to S$3,200 (commensurate with experience)</p></li><li><p>Location: Gul Circle (West)</p></li><li><p>Working Days: Monday to Friday (5 days)</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: Mon–Thu: 8:45am – 5:45pm, Fri: 8:45am – 5:15pm</p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>Accounts Payable (AP)</p><ul><li>Handle Accounts Payable processing and maintain accurate records with full supporting documents</li><li>Perform AP data entry and prepare payment runs</li><li>Track and record monthly prepayment schedules</li><li>Perform monthly AP and inter-company reconciliation</li><li>Support monthly financial closing activities and yearly audit requirements</li><li>Maintain proper filing system and assist with general administrative duties</li><li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Costing / Reporting</p><ul><li>Prepare monthly job orders reports</li><li>Assist in gathering monthly production output data</li><li>Prepare and monitor raw materials movement (actual vs budget)</li><li>Update and monitor commercial status on internal system (e.g., cost price, RFQ status, potential orders)</li><li>Support preparation of commercial quotations</li><li>Assist with monthly material and overhead analysis</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Finance / Accountancy or related discipline</li><li>Minimum 1–3 years of relevant experience in Accounts Payable (AP)</li><li>Exposure to costing is preferred; candidates without costing experience but willing to learn are welcome</li><li>Knowledge of ERP systems is advantageous</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills</li><li>Able to work independently and meet deadlines in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p>Interested candidate may submit full resume to <strong>6990 0458 (WhatsApp – Jiawen)</strong> and only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS Words format by using the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you give consent to collection, use and disclosure of your personal data and/or resume by the company (or its agent) for the purpose of the processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p>https://www.mci.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MCI-Job-Applicant-Data-Protection-Notice.pdf</p><p><strong>Yong Jia Wen</strong></p><p><strong>Registration Number: R25146805</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No: 13C6730 (MCI Consulting Pte Ltd)</strong></p>",
